## 1. Coverage Overview

{% set annotated = profiles | filter(attribute="status", value="complete") | length %}
{% set partial = profiles | filter(attribute="status", value="partial") | length %}
{% set missing = profiles | filter(attribute="status", value="missing") | length %}
{% set total = profiles | length %}
{% set coverage_pct = total > 0 ? (annotated + partial) * 100 / total : 0 %}

| Metric | Value |
|--------|-------|
| **Total Elements** | {{ total }} |
| **Fully Annotated** | {{ annotated }} |
| **Partially Annotated** | {{ partial }} |
| **Missing Annotations** | {{ missing }} |
| **Coverage** | {{ "%.0f" | format(coverage_pct) }}% |

### Coverage Progress Bar

```
{% set filled = (coverage_pct / 5) | round(method="floor") | int %}
{% for i in range(end=20) %}{% if i < filled %}{% elif i == filled %}{% else %}{% endif %}{% endfor %} {{ "%.0f" | format(coverage_pct) }}%
```

Legend: `█` Annotated | `░` Missing

