## 6. Annotation Health

> This section highlights elements that need attention. **Missing** elements have no explorer annotations. **Partial** elements have some but not all recommended annotations.

### Missing Annotations

{% set missing_profiles = profiles | filter(attribute="status", value="missing") | sort(attribute="elementType") %}
{% if missing_profiles | length > 0 %}
| Type | Name | IRI |
|------|------|-----|
{% for p in missing_profiles %}
| {{ p.elementType }} | **{{ p.elementName }}** | `<{{ p.elementIri }}>` |
{% endfor %}

**{{ missing_profiles | length }} element(s)** need explorer annotations.
{% else %}
All elements have explorer annotations.
{% endif %}

### Partial Annotations

{% set partial_profiles = profiles | filter(attribute="status", value="partial") | sort(attribute="elementType") %}
{% if partial_profiles | length > 0 %}
| Type | Name | IRI | Widget | Tooltip |
|------|------|-----|--------|---------|
{% for p in partial_profiles %}
| {{ p.elementType }} | **{{ p.elementName }}** | `<{{ p.elementIri }}>` | {{ p.widgetType }} | {{ p.tooltip }} |
{% endfor %}

**{{ partial_profiles | length }} element(s)** have partial annotations. Consider adding `exp:tooltip`, `exp:icon`, and verifying `exp:importance`.
{% else %}
No partially annotated elements.
{% endif %}

